com.appdynamics.instrumentation.sdk

Class ASDKPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appdynamics.instrumentation.sdk.ASDKPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRuleAppliable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ADataCollector, AGenericInterceptor, AInfoPoint, AMidDataCollector, AOutOfProcessCorrelator

    public abstract class ASDKPlugin
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRuleAppliable
    This is a common superclass for all SDK Plugin types. The logger and reflector will be set by the agent after construction of the plugin object, and should be available in every method other than the constructor. Created by ryan.terbush on 3/29/16.
